List of cards and what they do:

Knight: Move the robber, Steal 1 resource card from the owner of an adjacent settlement or city. (14/25)

Victory Point: 1 Victory Point! (5/25)

Road Builder: Place 2 new roads as if you had just built them. (2/25)

Monoply: When you play this card, announce 1 type of resouce. All other players must give you all their resource cards of that type. (2/25)

Year of Plenty: Take any 2 resources from the bank. Add them to your hand. They can be 2 of the same resource or 2 different resources. (2/25)


